Parliament, Tuesday, 5 May 2020 – The Portfolio Committee on Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities, and the Select Committee on Health and Social Services will today hold a virtual joint meeting to get a briefing from the Department of Women, Youth and Persons with Disabilities on its strategic, annual performance and budget plans for the 2020/21 financial year.
	
	Details of the virtual meeting:
	Date : 5 May 2020
	Time : 14:00pm
	
	The meeting will take place via Microsoft Teams meeting.
	
	Members of the media who would like to be part of the meeting to observe, can join Microsoft Teams Meeting link below or alternately connect via dialling the number provided below the link,
	
	Join Microsoft Teams Meeting
	+27 21 834 5669 South Africa, Cape Town (Toll)
	Conference ID: 766 453 068#
	
